nodes.text: A half-breed Massassi lived on Korriban around 3993 BBY and knew where to find a terentatek on the planet. Duron Qel-Droma and Shaela Nuur, who were on Korriban on a mission for the Jedi Order, looking for a terentatek were informed about this half-breed Massassi by a Ithorian and Quarren in the local cantina of Dreshdae.
